p.k: When Mick s fianc , Nicolette, gets into a horrific car crash, he s absolutely devastated. After weeks of waiting to hear if she ll make a full recovery, Nicolette surprises Mick by showing up at their home in perfectly good health with one small catch her face is completely covered in bandages. Nicolette explains that her doctors had to perform extensive surgery to save her life there s a significant chance she may look a little different. After removing the bandages, Mick is thrilled to discover that his fianc has been totally bimbofied! But that s not all that s changed - while Nicolette was planning on saving herself for marriage pre-car crash, her priorities have changed since her extreme transformation. She needs to get her fill of sexual satisfaction, stat!
